{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Revelation",
  "title": "A Revelation",
  "summary": "The luminescent, semi-transparent reporter Loy Marin of IGNews answers a return call from the businessman Smitherbodkins, who sits at his Corellia desk with a stack of papers. Loy congratulates him and offers his read on recent events -- that things are never what they appear and that Smitherbodkins and Qwynt are not, as it might seem, working together. Smitherbodkins plays a recording of the Direx boardroom incident, narrating his own near-fatal plunge with dark amusement, and confirms Loy can see where he is going: he wants a story. He reveals his real news -- that in three days it will be announced he has acquired the Corellian Engineering Corporation, explaining his presence on Corellia. Pouring himself a rich amber drink, Smitherbodkins all but declares he is going to war over the shipyards, and Loy agrees that hope amid conflict makes a fine story. The reporter bows formally and, with a crackle of his unstable image, reaches toward something on his end and vanishes from the galaxy.",
